  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nGot this error syncing lightclient from finalized foot of epoch 86000\r\n```\r\nError sync {} Error: Invalid aggregate signature\r\n    at assertValidSignedHeader (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/lodestar/packages/light-client/src/validation.ts:161:11)\r\n    at assertValidLightClientUpdate (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/lodestar/packages/light-client/src/validation.ts:51:3)\r\n    at Lightclient.processSyncCommitteeUpdate (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/lodestar/packages/light-client/src/index.ts:458:33)\r\n    at Lightclient.sync (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/lodestar/packages/light-client/src/index.ts:248:14)\r\n    at Lightclient.runLoop (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/lodestar/packages/light-client/src/index.ts:274:11)\r\n```\r\n\r\n`signedHeaderRoot=0x5ff5d5f10b63f56b5a032ffe53f082d3cead4f627a4e1003eccb157d197be6b5, signedHeaderSlot=2785278`\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nNo error\r\n\r\n",
